  • Annotation Types 
    Annotation Type Description
    net.jqwik.api.constraints.Unique
    Replace with annotation UniqueElements on container (List, Set, Stream, Iterator and array) parameter. Will be removed in version 1.5.0.
  • Methods 
    Method Description
    net.jqwik.api.Arbitraries.constant​(T)
    Use Arbitraries.just(Object) instead. To be removed in version 1.5.0.
    net.jqwik.api.Arbitrary.isUnique()
    Do not use. Will be removed in 1.5.0
    net.jqwik.api.Arbitrary.unique()
    Replace with uniqueElements() call on containing container arbitrary. Will be removed in 1.5.0.
